metadata.name: I HAVE A DREAM
metadata.description:
I HAVE A DREAM
Last night I had a nightmare ...  our beautiful world is ruled by crazy politicians ... They oppress, shed blood and people are crushed like pieces of meat under their hands and feet ..... A mother with a sharp  knife!!!... I read in the newspaper last night! .. and the child who was no longer alive! .... was horrible !... and this is what happened to the world .. I do not know how real it is and how much just in my nightmare. .. but sometimes dream and reality become one .!

more than sometimes....!
